    (9)    TM  ::=  TM "and" TM   (L-associative)
    (10)   TM  ::=  TM "=>" TM  [case_arrow__magic]   (R-associative)
    (50)   TM  ::=  TM "##" TM | TM "," TM   (R-associative)
    (70)   TM  ::=  "if" TM "then" TM "else" TM  [COND]
    (80)   TM  ::=  TM ":-" TM   (non-associative)
    (100)  TM  ::=  TM "=" TM   (non-associative)
