\bigskip

\begin{itemize}
\item where $t[\sigma_1,\ \ldots\ ,\sigma_n/\alpha_1,\ \ldots\ ,\alpha_n]$
denotes the result of substituting (in parallel) the types $\sigma_1$,
$\ldots$\ , $\sigma_n$ for the type variables $\alpha_1$, $\ldots$\ ,
